<doc id="1135534" wikidata="Q3244274" url="?curid=1135534" title="List of people related to Cajun music">
<text>This is a list of notable Cajun musicians, Cajun music instrument makers, Cajun music folklorists, Cajun music historians, and Cajun music activists.

